AMAL Channel 1
a simple mouse chase example on two channels

channel one
follow the mouse jerkily without autotest

Let X=130; Let Y=50;
Animate 0,(0,4)(1,4)(2,4)(1,4);
Back:
	Let R0=XM-14; Let R1=YM-14;
	Move R0-X, R1-Y, 20;
Jump Back

